ALTER TABLE main.bi_db.gold_sql_dp_prod_we_bi_db_dbo_bi_db_ddr_customer_periodic_status ALTER COLUMN PlayerLevelID_ThisWeek COMMENT 'Rolling `Week` slice `DateID BETWEEN @weekstartInt AND @dateInt` (with `@weekstart DATE = DATEADD(week, DATEDIFF(ww, 0, @date), -1)`): pulls from sibling `BI_DB_dbo.BI_DB_DDR_Customer_Daily_Status`.`PlayerLevelID`. Verbatim Snapshot meaning: Account tier: 4=demo, other values=real tiers. DEFAULT 0. Source: Ext_FSC_Real_Customer_Customer.PlayerLevelID (CC). FK to Dim_PlayerLevel. Critical field for interpreting `IsValidCustomer`. Inner `ACTIVETYPEPREP`: for static snapshot attributes SP uses `MAX(CASE WHEN <window> AND rn=1 THEN column END)` where `rn=1` is `ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY RealCID ORDER BY DateID DESC)` within `DateID BETWEEN @yearstartInt AND @dateInt` - i.e., the **`@date`** daily slice. Outer insert applies `SUM(..)`/`GROUP BY` but each customer/date collapses to a scalar duplicate of that daily value. `(Tier 2 - DWH_dbo.SP_Fact_SnapshotCustomer)`. Periodic reshape (Tier 2 - BI_DB_dbo.SP_DDR_Customer_Periodic_Status)';
